name: 2017 Women's March Attendance by US City
content:
Description: Estimates of crowd size / attendance of Women's March participants in January 2017, by US City.

[Source](https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1xa0iLqYKz8x9Yc_rfhtmSOJQ2EGgeUVjvV4A8LsIaxY/edit#gid=0)

Columns:

* City (string): What city the participants marched in
* State (string): State the aforementioned city is in
* Low estimate (numerical): Low estimate of the attendance count, per source(s)
* Best guess (numerical): Best guess of the attendance count, per source(s)
* High estimate (numerical): High estimate of the attendance count, per source(s)
* Source1 (string): where the estimates are sourced from
